        public static String toPackageName(String voiceName)
        Convert an arbitrary string into a valid java package name, as follows: - any characters that are not alphanumeric or underscore are deleted; - if the first character after a deleted one is a letter, it is capitalised. - if the first character is not a letter, we prepend a "V" for "voice".
